title: Grace Harlowe's Sophomore Year at High School
creator: Jessie Graham Flower
description: LibriVox recording of Grace Harlowe's Sophomore Year at High School, by Jessie Graham Flower. Read by Christine Blachford. Being a good and loyal friend is not easy, and Grace learns it the hard way. But, as in all children's books, good triumphs over evil. (Summary by Stav Nisser.) For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
